OL,3,CNoel Clarke set to learn outcome of
OL,4,Clibel claim against Guardian publisher
OL,6,FActor Noel Clarke is set to discover
OL,7,Fwhether he has been successful in his
OL,8,FHigh Court libel claim against the
OL,9,Fpublisher of the Guardian on Friday.
OL,11,FClarke, 49, is suing Guardian News and
OL,12,FMedia (GNM) over seven articles and a
OL,13,Fpodcast, including an article in April
OL,14,F2021 that said 20 women who knew him
OL,15,Fprofessionally had come forward with
OL,16,Fallegations of misconduct.
OL,18,FClarke denies the allegations, while
OL,19,FGNM is defending its reporting as
OL,20,Fbeing both true and in the public
OL,21,Finterest.
