OL,6,FMrs Justice Steyn is set to hand down
OL,7,Fher ruling at 10.30am on Friday.
OL,9,FThe trial of the libel claim was held
OL,10,Ffrom early March to early April at the
OL,11,FRoyal Courts of Justice in London.
OL,13,FClarke, who has previously appeared in
OL,14,FTV shows including Doctor Who, Auf
OL,15,FWiedersehen, Pet and Bulletproof, gave
OL,16,Fevidence over several days.
OL,18,FAt one stage, he appeared visibly
OL,19,Femotional as he claimed the publisher
OL,20,Fhad "smashed my life".
