OL,6,FHe said: "They have smashed my life
OL,7,Ffor four years with this rubbish, this
OL,8,Fnonsense. Four years."
OL,10,FHe continued: "I did not do this, I
OL,11,Fwould not do this. I have got
OL,12,Fchildren. This is not true."
OL,14,FHe later said that while he was "a
OL,15,Fflawed guy", he added: "The reason I
OL,16,Fstand here four years later is I am
OL,17,Fnot what they have branded me."
