OL,6,FPhilip Williams, representing the
OL,7,Factor, said that his client was a
OL,8,F"casualty" of a media "purge"
OL,9,Ffollowing the emergence of the MeToo
OL,10,Fmovement.
OL,12,FHe continued that Clarke was made a
OL,13,F"scapegoat" and was an "easy target"
OL,14,Fbecause he was at the height of his
OL,15,Fsuccess when the media industry
OL,16,F"zealously sought to correct itself".
